<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Intus — Psicologia positiva, filosofia, evidenza</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Una pagina editoriale elegante su psicologia positiva, filosofia e scienza, progettata per favorire lettura profonda, fiducia e ritorno spontaneo." />
  <meta name="theme-color" content="#f7f3ec" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #f7f3ec;
      --paper: rgba(255,255,255,0.72);
      --paper-strong: rgba(255,255,255,0.92);
      --ink: #1d1b19;
      --muted: #6c655d;
      --line: rgba(29,27,25,0.08);
      --accent: #8a6240;
      --accent-2: #274c47;
      --gold: #af8f55;
      --shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(28, 24, 18, 0.10);
      --radius-xl: 28px;
      --radius-lg: 22px;
      --radius-md: 16px;
      --max: 1240px;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Inter, system-ui, sans-serif;
      color: var(--ink);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(175,143,85,0.15), transparent 30%),
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(39,76,71,0.12), transparent 32%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #f8f5ef 0%, #f3eee5 100%);
      line-height: 1.65;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }

    .progress {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      height: 4px;
      width: 0%;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent), var(--gold), var(--accent-2));
      z-index: 999;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(138,98,64,0.35);
    }

    .container {
      width: min(calc(100% - 32px), var(--max));
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .nav-wrap {
      position: sticky;
      top: 14px;
      z-index: 50;
      padding-top: 14px;
    }

    nav {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 24px;
      padding: 14px 18px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.68);
      backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
      border-radius: 999px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .brand {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: var(--ink);
    }

    .brand-mark {
      width: 42px;
      height: 42px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", serif;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #fff;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-2), var(--accent));
      box-shadow: inset 0 0 30px rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    }

    .brand-text strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 0.98rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    }

    .brand-text span {
      display: block;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 18px;
      align-items: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .nav-links a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      transition: 180ms ease;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover,
    .nav-links a:focus-visible {
      color: var(--ink);
    }

    .btn {
      appearance: none;
      border: 0;
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 12px 18px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform 180ms ease, box-shadow 180ms ease, opacity 180ms ease;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .btn:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); }
    .btn:active { transform: translateY(0); }

    .btn-primary {
      color: #fff;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-2), var(--accent));
      box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(39,76,71,0.20);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      color: var(--ink);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
    }

    header.hero {
      padding: 58px 0 34px;
      min-height: 92vh;
      display: grid;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .hero-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.15fr 0.85fr;
      gap: 36px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(138,98,64,0.18);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
      border-radius: 999px;
      color: var(--accent-2);
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    h1, h2, h3 {
      margin: 0;
      line-height: 1.02;
      letter-spacing: -0.035em;
    }

    h1 {
      font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", serif;
      font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 7vw, 6.3rem);
      font-weight: 600;
      max-width: 12ch;
    }

    .hero-copy p {
      max-width: 62ch;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 1.06rem;
      margin: 22px 0 0;
    }

    .hero-actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 14px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: 28px;
    }

    .meta-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 14px;
      margin-top: 34px;
    }

    .meta-card,
    .panel,
    .quote-card,
    .article-card,
    .newsletter,
    .principle,
    .footer-card {
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: var(--paper);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .meta-card {
      padding: 18px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    }

    .meta-card strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .meta-card span {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.92rem;
    }

    .hero-side {
      display: grid;
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .panel {
      border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .feature-panel {
      padding: 28px;
      position: relative;
      min-height: 460px;
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.88), rgba(255,255,255,0.66)),
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(175,143,85,0.16), transparent 34%),
        radial-gradient(circle at bottom left, rgba(39,76,71,0.14), transparent 38%);
    }

    .feature-panel::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 18px;
      border-radius: 24px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(29,27,25,0.06);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .feature-panel small {
      color: var(--muted);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .feature-panel h2 {
      margin-top: 14px;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.1rem);
      font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", serif;
      font-weight: 600;
      max-width: 10ch;
    }

    .feature-panel p {
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 45ch;
      margin-top: 16px;
    }

    .insight-stack {
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-top: 26px;
    }

    .insight {
      display: flex;
      gap: 14px;
      align-items: flex-start;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.74);
      border: 1px solid rgba(29,27,25,0.06);
    }

    .insight b {
      display: block;
      font-size: 0.96rem;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .insight span {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .orb {
      width: 42px;
      height: 42px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      flex: 0 0 42px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(39,76,71,0.18), rgba(138,98,64,0.22));
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--accent-2);
    }

    section {
      padding: 44px 0;
    }

    .section-head {
      display: flex;
      align-items: end;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 22px;
    }

    .section-head h2 {
      font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", serif;
      font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 4rem);
      font-weight: 600;
      max-width: 10ch;
    }

    .section-head p {
      max-width: 56ch;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin: 0;
    }

    .split {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 0.8fr 1.2fr;
      gap: 24px;
      align-items: start;
    }

    .quote-card {
      border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
      padding: 30px;
      min-height: 100%;
      position: sticky;
      top: 100px;
    }

    .quote-card .kicker {
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      color: var(--accent);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .quote-card blockquote {
      margin: 18px 0 14px;
      font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", serif;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.7vw, 2.8rem);
      line-height: 1.02;
    }

    .quote-card p {
      color: var(--muted);
      margin: 0;
    }

    .articles {
      display: grid;
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .article-card {
      padding: 24px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      transition: transform 180ms ease, border-color 180ms ease, background 180ms ease;
    }

    .article-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      border-color: rgba(138,98,64,0.18);
      background: var(--paper-strong);
    }

    .article-top {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .tag-row {
      display: flex;
      gap: 8px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .tag {
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 8px 10px;
      background: rgba(39,76,71,0.08);
      color: var(--accent-2);
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    }

    .article-card h3 {
      font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      max-width: 18ch;
    }

    .article-card p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 62ch;
    }

    .article-footer {
      margin-top: 18px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 14px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.92rem;
    }

    .principles-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .principle {
      padding: 24px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    }

    .principle strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .principle p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .newsletter {
      border-radius: calc(var(--radius-xl) + 8px);
      padding: 34px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
      gap: 24px;
      align-items: end;
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.88), rgba(255,255,255,0.78)),
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(175,143,85,0.18), transparent 30%);
    }

    .newsletter h2 {
      font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", serif;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
      font-weight: 600;
      max-width: 12ch;
    }

    .newsletter p {
      margin: 10px 0 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 58ch;
    }

    .form {
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: end;
    }

    .form input {
      min-width: min(100%, 320px);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.88);
      padding: 14px 16px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font: inherit;
      color: var(--ink);
      outline: none;
      transition: box-shadow 180ms ease, border-color 180ms ease;
    }

    .form input:focus {
      border-color: rgba(39,76,71,0.22);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(39,76,71,0.08);
    }

    footer {
      padding: 18px 0 56px;
    }

    .footer-card {
      border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
      padding: 22px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
      gap: 20px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .footer-card p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .footer-links {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: end;
      gap: 16px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .footer-links a {
      color: var(--ink);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      opacity: 0.8;
    }

    .footer-links a:hover { opacity: 1; }

    .reveal {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(18px);
      transition: opacity 600ms ease, transform 600ms ease;
    }

    .reveal.visible {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }

    @media (max-width: 1080px) {
      .hero-grid,
      .split,
      .newsletter,
      .footer-card,
      .principles-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .quote-card { position: relative; top: 0; }
      .form { justify-content: start; }
      .footer-links { justify-content: start; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 780px) {
      .nav-links { display: none; }
      .meta-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      h1 { max-width: 11ch; }
      .feature-panel { min-height: auto; }
      .section-head { align-items: start; flex-direction: column; }
    }

    @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
      html { scroll-behavior: auto; }
      * { transition: none !important; animation: none !important; }
      .reveal { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="progress" id="progress"></div>

  <div class="container nav-wrap">
    <nav aria-label="Navigazione principale">
      <a href="#top" class="brand" aria-label="Intus home">
        <div class="brand-mark">I</div>
        <div class="brand-text">
          <strong>Intus</strong>
          <span>Psicologia positiva, filosofia, pratica</span>
        </div>
      </a>
      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="#manifesto">Manifesto</a>
        <a href="#articoli">Articoli</a>
        <a href="#metodo">Metodo</a>
        <a href="#lettera">Lettera</a>
      </div>
      <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#lettera">Ricevi un saggio</a>
    </nav>
  </div>

  <header class="hero container" id="top">
    <div class="hero-grid">
      <div class="hero-copy reveal">
        <div class="eyebrow">Scienza, profondità, bellezza cognitiva</div>
        <h1>La mente fiorisce dove il pensiero non viene semplificato.</h1>
        <p>
          Intus è una casa editoriale digitale dedicata alla psicologia positiva intelligente: non slogan,
          non ottimismo superficiale, ma ricerca, filosofia, attenzione al linguaggio e idee che trasformano
          il modo in cui una persona comprende il proprio benessere.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#articoli">Inizia a leggere</a>
          <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#manifesto">Perché esistiamo</a>
        </div>
        <div class="meta-row">
          <article class="meta-card reveal">
            <strong>Approccio rigoroso</strong>
            <span>Ogni tesi parte da studi, limiti metodologici e applicazioni concrete.</span>
          </article>
          <article class="meta-card reveal">
            <strong>Esperienza calma</strong>
            <span>Nessuna frizione inutile: leggibilità, ritmo, pause visive e comfort cognitivo.</span>
          </article>
          <article class="meta-card reveal">
            <strong>Relazione duratura</strong>
            <span>Il ritorno nasce da fiducia, identità editoriale e utilità reale, non da pressione.</span>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>

      <aside class="hero-side reveal" aria-label="Anteprima editoriale">
        <div class="panel feature-panel">
          <small>Edizione inaugurale</small>
          <h2>Come costruire una vita buona senza raccontarsela.</h2>
          <p>
            Un percorso tra gratitudine, autodeterminazione, senso, virtù, limiti del self-help e pratiche
            che migliorano il benessere senza infantilizzare il lettore.
          </p>
          <div class="insight-stack">
            <div class="insight">
              <div class="orb">01</div>
              <div>
                <b>Evidenza prima della promessa</b>
                <span>Mostriamo ciò che funziona, per chi, quando e con quali cautele.</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="insight">
              <div class="orb">02</div>
              <div>
                <b>Piacere della lettura</b>
                <span>Tipografia, spazi, progressione narrativa e micro-ritmi per favorire immersione.</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="insight">
              <div class="orb">03</div>
              <div>
                <b>Persuasione etica</b>
                <span>Inviti chiari e onesti, senza scorciatoie manipolative o pattern oscuri.</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section id="manifesto">
      <div class="container split">
        <aside class="quote-card reveal">
          <div class="kicker">Manifesto</div>
          <blockquote>
            La psicologia positiva migliore non ti vende euforia. Ti offre strumenti per abitare la realtà con più lucidità, forza e gentilezza.
          </blockquote>
          <p>
            Qui il lettore viene trattato come una persona intelligente: capace di sfumature, dubbi, profondità e desiderio autentico di comprensione.
          </p>
        </aside>

        <div class="articles">
          <article class="article-card reveal">
            <div class="article-top">
              <div class="tag-row">
                <span class="tag">Psicologia positiva</span>
                <span class="tag">Scienza applicata</span>
              </div>
              <span>06 min</span>
            </div>
            <h3>Non parliamo di felicità performativa.</h3>
            <p>
              Parliamo di benessere come competenza: regolazione emotiva, significato, agency, relazioni, attenzione, abitudini e contesto.
              Il tono del sito evita la banalizzazione perché un lettore colto resta più a lungo quando percepisce densità, onestà intellettuale e una promessa mantenuta.
            </p>
            <div class="article-footer">
              <span>Più profondità, meno rumore</span>
              <a href="#articoli" class="btn btn-secondary">Vedi esempi</a>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="article-card reveal">
            <div class="article-top">
              <div class="tag-row">
                <span class="tag">Filosofia</span>
                <span class="tag">Etica del vivere</span>
              </div>
              <span>08 min</span>
            </div>
            <h3>La buona vita è anche una questione di forma.</h3>
            <p>
              Aristotele, gli Stoici, Simone Weil, Martha Nussbaum e la tradizione fenomenologica mostrano che il benessere non è soltanto stato interno,
              ma qualità del rapporto con il mondo. Il sito riflette questa visione: sobrio, colto, contemplativo, invitante.
            </p>
            <div class="article-footer">
              <span>Il design diventa argomento</span>
              <a href="#metodo" class="btn btn-secondary">Scopri il metodo</a>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="article-card reveal">
            <div class="article-top">
              <div class="tag-row">
                <span class="tag">UX editoriale</span>
                <span class="tag">Trust</span>
              </div>
              <span>05 min</span>
            </div>
            <h3>Far tornare il lettore senza spingerlo.</h3>
            <p>
              Il ritorno non viene forzato con urgenza artificiale, notifiche aggressive o trappole cognitive. Nasce da ritmo, riconoscibilità, promessa editoriale,
              segnalazione del valore e continuità tematica. Un sito memorabile riduce l'attrito e aumenta la fiducia.
            </p>
            <div class="article-footer">
              <span>Retention attraverso comfort e qualità</span>
              <a href="#lettera" class="btn btn-secondary">Iscriviti</a>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="articoli">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-head reveal">
          <div>
            <div class="eyebrow">Esempi editoriali</div>
            <h2>Articoli pensati per restare.</h2>
          </div>
          <p>
            Ogni card è scritta per offrire una combinazione di chiarezza, autorevolezza, curiosità e applicabilità. Questo bilanciamento aiuta la lettura profonda e la propensione al ritorno.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="articles">
          <article class="article-card reveal">
            <div class="article-top">
              <div class="tag-row">
                <span class="tag">Ricerca</span>
                <span class="tag">Benessere</span>
                <span class="tag">Pratica</span>
              </div>
              <span>Articolo guida</span>
            </div>
            <h3>Gratitudine: quando funziona davvero e quando diventa retorica.</h3>
            <p>
              Un pezzo che parte dagli studi sulle pratiche di gratitudine, ne distingue gli effetti medi dai miti divulgativi e mostra come usare il journaling in modo realistico.
              L'angolo editoriale non è "pensa positivo", ma: impara a registrare il bene senza negare il male.
            </p>
            <div class="article-footer">
              <span>Con evidenze, limiti, protocollo di 7 giorni</span>
              <a href="#lettera" class="btn btn-secondary">Ricevi il PDF</a>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="article-card reveal">
            <div class="article-top">
              <div class="tag-row">
                <span class="tag">Motivazione</span>
                <span class="tag">Autodeterminazione</span>
